"以下的示例展示了转义字符的使用。以下两行代码都会打印 ``Hello\"World!``。推荐"
"使用转义字符来替代传统的 BlitzBasic 写法，因为转义字符是在编译期处理，并能减"
"少运行时的字符串对象数量。"

#: ../../basic-data-types.rst:72 ../../basic-data-types.rst:91
#: ../../basic-data-types.rst:99
msgid "Pointer"
msgstr "指针"

#: ../../basic-data-types.rst:74
msgid ""
"**Pointer** are objects that store a memory address. This type is for "
"solving that pointers are stored in an integer in BlitzBasic."
msgstr ""
"**指针** 是存储内存地址的对象。这种类型用于解决在 BlitzBasic 中指针存储在整数"
"中的问题。"

#: ../../basic-data-types.rst:76 ../../basic-data-types.rst:103
msgid ""
"When assigning a pointer to an integer variable, ZiYue4D will automatically "
"raise the variable to pointer type."
msgstr "在将指针分配给整数变量时，ZiYue4D 会自动将该变量提升为指针类型。"

#: ../../basic-data-types.rst:79
msgid "Implicit conversion"
msgstr "隐式转换"

#: ../../basic-data-types.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Implicit conversion** plays an important role in ZiYue4D. Most of the "
"conversion in ZiYue4D is implicit, and observes the same rules as in "
"BlitzBasic."
msgstr ""
"**隐式转换** 在ZiYue4D中扮演着重要的角色。大多数的转换在ZiYue4D中是隐式的，并"
"且与BlitzBasic是一样的。"

